</p>
                        <p>Poor impression of a personal ovoid seal (f. 14r): <persName key="person_f7248" role="asn">Mādhavdās</persName> […]. 
                        </p>
                        <p>Note at end indicating the work had been collated by <persName key="person_f7011" role="crr">ʿAbd al-Bāqī</persName>. 
                        </p>
