                        <p>Fragment of a larger compendium of works by the poet and Ṣūfī leader, <persName key="viaf_33415216" role="aut">Nūr al-Dīn Niʿmat Allāh ibn ʿAbd Allāh ibn Muḥammad al-Ḥusaynī al-Kirmānī</persName>, commonly known as <persName key="viaf_33415216" role="aut">Niʿmat Allāh "Valī"</persName> (d. 834/1431). 
                        </p>
                        <p>The fragment is defective at the beginning and is comprised of several portions of heterogeneous origins and nastaʿlīq hands running in continued succession, with corresponding catchwords. 
</p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
